h3: Selected Case Studies

I don’t bridge the gap between design and code. I eliminate it.

With decades of experience leading newsrooms and building digital products, I help organizations transform complex information into clear, scalable, and profitable experiences.

Below is a curated selection of case studies where strategy, design, and technology converge to solve real business problems.

{.bloco}
{imagem}
