h4: ATBL Enterprise App 

While <em>Estadão</em> shows my capacity for scale, <em><a href="https://www.atbl.com.br/loja">ATBL</a></em> demonstrates my hands-on engineering skills. I built a Progressive Web App (PWA) to replace manual spreadsheets with a synchronized digital ecosystem.<br><br><strong>Tech Stack:</strong> Svelte, Node.js API integration with Sankhya ERP.

<strong>Result:</strong> By placing stock control, sales orders, and dashboards in the employees' pockets, the company saw a <strong>12.5% revenue increase</strong> through improved efficiency.
{}

