h4: Rota +Segura (Safer Route)

Data visualization meets utility. I art directed and helped to develop <a href="https://www.estadao.com.br/sao-paulo/rota-segura-ferramenta-permite-tracar-os-trajetos-com-menos-roubos-de-veiculos/?srsltid=AfmBOooXdh0fkdsebXkWtlldozl_OYs2mpJLvWXN7RHT5cYLSuw0ipEM" target="_blank">this interactive map</a> allowing citizens to find safer driving routes in São Paulo based on crime data. It uses custom algorithms to filter incidents by time, vehicle type, and location, turning raw database statistics into actionable personal safety advice.
{}

