h4: Malofiej Gold Medal: Tapuiassauro.

Winner of the <em>"Oscar of Infographics"</em>. We reconstructed a newly discovered Brazilian titanosaur species. <a href="https://www.estadao.com.br/infograficos/tapuiassauro-o-novo-dinossauro-do-brasil,ciencia,280832?srsltid=AfmBOoo58RzUTw-l2HjrOekBdRm_lSls0kpa5_w8zI6A8IRItyRI-Eqq" target="_blank">This project</a> exemplifies my ability to translate complex scientific data into accessible, engaging visual formats.
