h4: The Semantics of Power

A <a href="https://www.estadao.com.br/infograficos/politica,graficos-mostram-temas-dos-discursos-de-posse-desde-volta-das-diretas,955154?srsltid=AfmBOoqXKOpHYD7a00RP2u9XjpPhcQwNd7FZz3nWgIAKloHGlAI6AxA0" target="_blank">visual analysis of presidential inaugural speeches</a> since Brazil's redemocratization. Using Natural Language Processing (NLP) concepts applied to visual design to reveal political shifts through vocabulary size and keyword frequency.
