h4: Favela Amazônia: Portrait of a New Forest

Winner of the SIP (Inter American Press Association) Award. A deep-dive investigation into the urbanization of the <a href="https://infograficos.estadao.com.br/especiais/favela-amazonia/" target="_blank">Amazon rainforest</a>.

My role was to create a visual atmosphere that conveyed the tension and complexity of the region without sensationalism.
