h4:'The Drummer’s Movement' Book

Complete art direction and layout for <em>André Polvo’s instructional methodology</em>, teacher and drummer of Preta Gil, The Masked Singer Brazil, among others.

A project focused on rhythm-visual and musical-translating sound concepts into graphic notation.
